  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d659aa9d-a9ff-4046-8f9b-106cadd76e8c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a747b353-a4b2-48f9-a6e7-bacb1916d98d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f89d57a9-e0bc-4fce-b635-655276ab1c93\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>낱장형 인쇄물 : 리플렛</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-74a01c22-766a-4dce-9ab6-078701e1dde2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-db1af903-4a63-4be3-92cf-895215de5167\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-90776026-aa2f-49ee-bcee-2364206416fb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">보통 A4 3단 접지라고 하면 A4를 3번 접어서 만드는 사이즈를 말합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0a58bd64-cb37-4ec1-a379-668bffbac259\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-73c0a153-09ca-4b56-935c-252d536d7afa\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-08dfbc2c-165e-4a67-8a89-ba254bb7991b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-a446e4b0-9dae-475b-965c-065604e84535\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7696eb99-8abd-4260-8a1b-d5998e5511c5\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이번에는 접으면 A4가 되는 사이즈의 인쇄물을 알아 보겠습니다. 다음 인쇄물은 저희가 인쇄만을 작업한 건입니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-37d8f6e6-b871-461e-9bbf-f0dbcad78bba\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-874bcab3-4a9b-4dd1-9000-06bdeeb8c04f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-47b630cc-718b-4d58-aeeb-9b477c999936\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-5394c93e-b984-4cc5-a566-4682fae571d8\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222919465795/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222919465795/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222919465795/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-11810d70-0298-4b36-8634-fe28af383a97\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-eeca3dea-9870-4c77-967a-87f470808c32\" style=\"\">사진 목업</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-75256372-c1ca-4892-a789-d9c7dcecf64b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-504194e5-b9f1-40fa-9519-877f6957a80c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0545e260-b3ec-4efd-9237-269f3851d161\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f982525f-0b8d-47ad-98af-979b9b6a49ad\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>디자인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-6b91f74b-2ebe-4125-aaf6-79b39e7e111f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d36d05da-9104-46ea-a741-10035e21dddc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">원고 : 선방 제공</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-00b0f7e3-8fdc-49d5-b4c1-b66d374e2e24\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5e7a9c84-cfff-4cc1-91d0-6dffdc380434\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">전체 디자인 파일은 PDF형태로 제공 받았습니다. 일부 내용 수정하여 작업하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-331dca30-60c4-44c6-9dbd-5486dfa45b35\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f9d97186-3afb-436d-b54a-846f7a71542f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ae4b3e76-8ca5-4b18-8c70-c151ce6fef07\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a2339ae0-9f68-4708-8c9b-095615931b6c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-8ef60c92-308b-4063-8507-576d8e47b1af\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-01fa8703-db53-4187-bb58-e005ec3a1a7c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">랑데뷰 백색 240g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-927c5deb-a8c1-48c9-a985-8d2428cb09b4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-175efaca-6c4e-48c9-9db7-7f09691d2369\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45081f76-be74-414d-aed1-10b4bee4f08a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-92bf9b62-8534-4895-adbe-618c7675feea\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>사이즈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-4c15de95-be82-4466-95e4-c6d3c756b4f6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dc1cd67e-e12e-43c1-95f2-35a0dd33ad3c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">국 3절 3단 접지 630mm × 294mm : 3단 접은 후 약 A4</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-f614884d-b4d2-4ada-ab62-b048b4fb2edf\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-de8f4499-7a22-4473-86a9-ea58de5176ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-58f1f7f7-9e5f-44f3-8705-fdd3be4928e2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-89ebbc35-f774-4f8d-96d2-095982d8b359\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>페이지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-58a1dfee-152c-4689-9638-38adbeb0c12f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3337a587-a6da-44a7-8c7d-d56ab0821e33\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">낱장형 양면 2pages : 접은 후 6pages</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-862ac11a-eaa8-41b5-94b0-84ea4f31f8d6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e6ff7a34-bba1-4d98-90ef-6b8a2bb11b3b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-50a9895c-2aac-476b-b218-a925ada65bb7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-406203dd-5eff-4046-b1f1-08b2d568999e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-e480f4e6-7d81-4d6d-95d0-5ca1d4ddb6b8\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-343d66e3-0fe2-402c-9dc5-1c68d1f77c89\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">양면 컬러4도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-de7e46cc-f490-464f-814e-e69ab5b08c2b\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-02b19721-8f23-41bf-a6fb-034f6dee7379\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1524c85a-14e2-4603-9ea2-cb218b4763da\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3298714a-a108-4c56-b084-08a53f9edd60\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>후가공</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-1b2d47f6-030d-4426-890e-905fc1a17bb5\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ef3870a4-a0fe-4886-a24f-72382e4b3943\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">3단 정접지, 오시 후 접지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-524e9a47-8fb3-4dae-a12a-204b089d3a9d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-44255d64-e569-4247-b494-207b7aa1756d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d84ccba4-ab0e-4460-9204-3c249ed077e9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5ed6f3b6-0d09-41e4-b839-85cf20ba5706\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1e411952-6054-4c3e-8fc6-cc305301b26b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-2ba8a962-c980-4fad-8995-f6994ee4e738\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3ec2e103-ebf9-4edd-9a70-a4cf1c0c1cd8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222919465795/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cb6a3738-3742-420f-a327-bb7c9a11e93f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-fc0f1472-7b0b-41bb-afe3-6bd2b139db0d\" style=\"\">전체 디자인</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-1623be90-7882-4b5e-b43d-ed6b70cc26d1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fde20710-d486-4af4-a20f-aea66122b2f2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-3b4fab90-bd7b-41a7-b884-1722031df476\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-667d68e7-e29a-4d70-a218-c5ef8c48c6fe\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">사이즈는 조판상 A4에서 약간 적은 사이즈였습니다. (297mm &gt; 294mm) 이 파일은 PDF로 인계받았으며 일부 내용 수정하여 작업하였습니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a7dce41f-325e-41ec-a527-08738ae71048\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니은 기존에 있는 인쇄데이터를 수정하여 작업이 가능합니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-45872661-126c-49be-af2c-1e0b9b6cd06b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> 특별한 사항이 아니면 수정비용없이 인쇄진행이 가능합니다. 저희가 디자인하지않고 작업한 몇 안되는 예시입니다. 다만 무조건 가격의 비딩으로만 진행하지는 않습니다. 기존 업체의 디자인만 주고 인쇄진행을 가격으로만 뺏어오는 것은 상도덕에 맞지 않습니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-fd70c99a-2122-4ef4-b03f-2d8e52a11eb1\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dbc2752e-49d0-4689-9372-9d8ad718b76b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-90772968-85e6-4333-8af6-8d439f492e9c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9df64660-960e-4696-a288-07db2518d986\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b1b33061-897d-445c-8066-bf3801f42cfc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-97a63258-ca12-4cdb-b3e0-f6e14b20b2b0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2d09df37-6d0e-43bb-8bff-cafc1ddcf5aa\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기존의 데이터는 보통 ai나 pdf파일로 인계를 받습니다. 기존의 데이터가 비트맵이미지인 png나 jpg파일은 해상도나 기타 인쇄시 수정이 불가능하므로 인쇄데이터로 적합하지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34f49ce7-6dca-43fa-87cf-35e4024e2531\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-47bd37f8-14d6-4d19-b420-0e42a50796f8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-345dba84-ad7b-4aed-b367-a7256d4e89b8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-157bbdde-c4a8-4950-8709-04610b402d8c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6a37eca0-5734-4756-a723-63aeca24f2e6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b43e705-f8cc-43bf-b13c-79aca93a1ba0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-08f9228a-1410-4497-86b9-d9adc07e0ffd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">반드시 ai, pdf, cdr등의 벡터 이미지를 보내주시기 바랍니다. 그리고 보내주실 때 서체를 레스터 라이징해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bde4a6aa-13d8-4eeb-9267-93b57be62b97\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222919465795/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-784c066e-d34a-411e-a3e4-d0865f079c2e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c0a289fc-6fb9-41dc-89b7-b914ee7530ee\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-74a44d72-dfb6-474e-a1f6-8a9ff9f8b81b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">서체가 윤곽선만들기로 바꿔서 보내지 않으면 서체가 살아있어서 변형이나 에러가 발생할 수 있습니다. 그러나 고객분들은 일러스트나 코렐드로우 사용자가 아니시죠? 모르셔도 됩니다. 그냥 (주)파파스컴퍼니에 문의만 해주시면 됩니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6a6dfad4-b973-45b8-8169-d661b60893bf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-00cca3c7-48cc-4721-91ac-a889c4a8d486\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8ffc1464-eaf5-4ac6-8b04-fd6038ecb9c7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}